{"tid":1384653,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再用小朋友、學生標籤前線義人","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T03:03:53.000Z","uid":279069,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2cde301314d30bc8da24b06b14cc2b7bfefdefd5","tid":1384653,"uid":279069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:31:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">標題可能有Ｄ搏屌，<br />\n但我最怕就係有人利用大家既善心用階級去分化抗爭者（大人/小朋友、成年人／學生）<br />\n之後政府就順理成章話係廢青攪事，扼殺晒全港人既努力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係邊個幫邊個，只係自發做好份內事</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有付出架，我地要以手足相稱。<br />\n唔好再用大人細路／打工仔學生哥去具分喇！<br />\n所有抗爭者都係手足，都係兄弟<br />\n所有抗爭者不分階級、性別、族裔和年齡。</span></span></strong><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"4e57e1c8343f314a9b9506507e353602663bfcbb","tid":1384653,"uid":167878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:32:41.000Z","msg":"大家由日常做起 預防分化<br />\n無論和理非定勇武都稱呼<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟 手足</span></span><br />\n可以團結香港人 我地香港人係兄弟"},{"pid":"b8e6335cb8212792c9054078b7360485aae591d2","tid":1384653,"uid":150079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:38:24.000Z","msg":"日本巴打繼續支持港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人"},{"pid":"fc61333c727d3c9a5a78a216555abe4b480a6433","tid":1384653,"uid":279069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:03:53.000Z","msg":"push push push"}]}